Add fiber asm for riscv64, sparc64 and powerpc64, to avoid
"configure: error: setcontext required but not found"

Index: libphobos/configure
--- libphobos/configure.orig
+++ libphobos/configure
@@ -692,8 +692,12 @@ DRUNTIME_CPU_SYSTEMZ_FALSE
 DRUNTIME_CPU_SYSTEMZ_TRUE
